description:
This is a 15 minute workout called 'A Message from Your Successful Future Self (Guided Meditation)' from the channel Great Meditation.
The workout falls under Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Deep Recharge vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Listening to this 15-minute guided meditation is a powerful way to connect with your successful future self and gain wisdom, clarity, and motivation.  Through gentle visualization, you’ll receive an inspiring message from the version of you who has already achieved your dreams, guiding you toward your highest potential.  At the same time, this meditation helps you release the weight of the past, letting go of anything that no longer serves you—doubt, fear, or regret—so you can move forward with confidence and ease.  Give yourself this moment of transformation and step into the limitless possibilities of your future

This is an Original guided meditation recorded by us.  

A special thank you to all our monthly supporters!  
We appreciate all your support and contribution to allow this channel to continue to share our guided meditations with the world.  Thank you!!!
